Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadySetException
    Exception throws when trying to set a variable already set.
    CannotSendEventException
    Exception thrown when an executer cannot execute itself.
    CheckQueueException
    Exception thrown by the Viewer when there is an event in the BlockingQueue to be server.
    EmptyQueueException
    Exception thrown by the Viewer when the BlockingQueue is empty.
    EndCardSelectionException
    Exception thrown when all the cards to be selected have been selected.
    NotFoundException
    Exception thrown when the searched ViewObject has not been found.
    WrongEventException
    Exception thrown when the ViewObject has been notified with an incorrect Event or a wrong event.
    WrongParametersException
    Exception thrown when the parameters set are incorrect.
    WrongViewObjectException
    Exception thrown when the searched ViewObject is of a different Class from the one on which is being searched.
